data.description: This delightful home in Donner Trails Estates has been freshly painted and ready for its new owner. Spacious kitchen with gas stove, dishwasher, refrigerator, painted oak cabinets and tile counters. Central air conditioning for those hot days. Vaulted ceilings and a fully fenced backyard with large back patio for entertaining; whether it's hosting barbecues, enjoying morning coffee, or simply relaxing in the fresh air.   Come see this great opportunity in Fernley today. Located centrally between highway 50 and Farm district road for easy access to town or highway. Close to schools, shopping, and a short drive to the Tesla Giga Factory. Home has been updated with a Day & Night 90% + gas furnace and an ultra high efficiency Navien tankless water heater. This home qualifies for an FHA assumable interest rate. Call for more details.
